<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cn">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>剪切板登录</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
  <div class="w-full max-w-sm bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mt-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-blue-700 mb-6">请输入剪切板密码</h2>
    <div class="mb-3 text-sm text-gray-600 bg-blue-50 rounded px-3 py-2 text-center">
      如该剪切板无密码，直接点击登录即可。
    </div>
    <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined') { %>
      <div class="mb-4 text-red-500 text-center"><%= error %></div>
    <% } %>
    <form method="post" action="/clipboard/<%= boardId %>/login" class="space-y-4">
      <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="密码（如无密码可留空）" class="w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400">
      <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white py-2 rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition">登录</button>
    </form>
    <a href="/" class="block w-full mt-4 bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 text-center py-2 rounded hover:bg-gray-300 transition">返回主页</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
